description: Talkpool AG engages in the provision of telecommunication services. The company is headquartered in Chur, Graubuenden and currently employs 1,142 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-05-24. The company delivers a comprehensive range of network design, engineering, implementation and managed services designs for telecommunications operators, system vendors and contractors. The firm also develops monitoring systems in buildings with real time applications for building owners and occupants. The company operates in approximately 15 countries, such as Switzerland, Germany, Sweden, the United States, Mexico, Haiti, Kenya, Tanzania, Zimbabwe, Uganda, Mauritius, Zambia, Botswana, Pakistan and Saudi Arabia. The firm operates through a global partnership of joint ventures and franchises.
name: TalkPool AG
